      "text": "Single chokepoint for ALL Python-tier LLM access — no direct provider SDK calls elsewhere. embed has NO\nper-call fallback: a down embedder parks the chunk in ingestion.dlq for retry with the original model\n(mixing embedding models within a Qdrant collection makes distances meaningless — FR-029).",
